additional_info:
Alternatively you can paste the css into Infinity chan/8chan settings.
Minus the first and last line:
@-moz-document domain('8ch.net') {
}

css:
@-moz-document domain('8ch.net') {
.theme-catalog div.grid-size-small {
max-height: 300px;
}
.theme-catalog div.grid-size-small img {
max-height: 100%;
max-width: 100%;
}
.theme-catalog div.thread img {
max-height: 100%;
max-width: 100%;
box-shadow: none;
border: 0px;
}
.theme-catalog div.threads {
margin-left: 0px;
}
}
